comments: Harris (BKN) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Capela (ATL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Capela (ATL) legally contests Curry's (BKN) jump shot attempt and incidental contact occurs once Curry has returned to the floor. Play resumes with a jump ball at center circle.
Irving (BKN) moves alongside Young's (ATL) path as he attempts to pass and marginal body contact occurs.
Forrest (ATL) moves alongside Irving's (BKN) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he contests during the driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) initiates contact with O'Neale's (BKN) arm that affects his SQBR.
Young (ATL) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Curry (BKN) at the end of the drive.
Curry (BKN) legally takes two steps after regathering the loose ball.
Durant (BKN) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Capela (ATL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Durant (BKN) keeps his hand behind the ball and doesn't bring it underneath the ball in between dribbles.
Johnson (ATL) commits a take foul on Curry (BKN).
Forrest (ATL) initiates body contact with Durant (BKN) that affects his SQBR.
Harris (BKN) closes out and marginal leg contact occurs with Bogdanovic's (ATL) as they come together at the start of the drive.
